                            </ol>
                        </li>
                        <li>If we refuse to execute the payment, we will notify you as soon as possible unless it would not be unlawful for us to do so. If possible, we will provide the reasons for refusal to execute the payment and where those reasons relate to factual matters, the procedure for rectifying any factual errors that led to such refusal.</li>
                        <li>The execution of any payment to or from your Account (including Card payments) may be delayed or refused due to the performance of Paynetics' security or legal compliance checks, including if Paynetics suspects that the payment is involved in fraudulent, illegal, or unacceptable activities or constitutes an unauthorized payment.</li>
