                    <h2 class="font-AeonikBlack text-lg md:text-xl xl:text-2xl 4xl:text-4xl uppercase mt-4">8. DESCRIPTION OF THE CARD</h2>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Your Card is issued to you by Paynetics and is linked to your Account in EUR or GBP, as applicable, maintained by Paynetics. Your Card can be used in your country of residence or abroad.</li>
