                        <li>Unless specified otherwise in this Agreement, your Card can be used to pay merchants for goods or services at (whether in-store, online or over the phone) and for cash withdrawals at ATMs. If you have been issued with a virtual Card, it can only be used to pay merchants online and for contactless payments. Your Card can be used at all card acceptance terminal devices bearing the Mastercard logo which maintain the necessary functions.</li>
