                            <li>If a payment is received in your Account incorrectly (for example, by mistake), Paynetics may, where it considers reasonable to do so, hold the payment and return it to the sender. In aliy case, Paynetics is obliged to provide certain information to the sender's payment service provider about you and the payment to enable them to recover the funds.</li>
                            <p><i><strong>Payments initiated by payee</strong></i></p>
