                    <h2 class="font-AeonikBlack text-lg md:text-xl xl:text-2xl 4xl:text-4xl uppercase mt-4">11. YOUR OBLIGATIONS TO KEEP THE PLATFORM AND YOUR CARD S SAFE</h2>
